responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "072DFC614F6F6DE3912C04AB5A8EE01A", "Haha! Do you not listen? It cannot be shattered. You must seek and shatter the Ward that keeps the Star\'s gates sealed tight. Do so and then you can destroy Ozu. All that must be done is to find the resting place of a thousand year old Star Ward and shatter it. Simple enough!")
